metadata.name: Lil neko friend #1
metadata.description:
Lil neko friends is a community driven collection of 5k randomly generated cats paying tribute to the traditional Japanese "maneki neko". 
  The project aims to bring awareness to mental health in a fast paced environment as the nft world.
  Hence the creation of a dedicated lo-fi music YouTube channel where the community can uplift each other and vibe with their lil neko friends.
  Holders will also have benefits for future collections.
